data.description: ATTENTION!!! $5,000 towards Buyers closing cost! This quaint 3 bedroom/1 Bathroom home is now available to be your new home! The block construction and almost on a 1/4 acre within city limits make this property unique. Tile floors throughout the main living areas and LVP wood flooring in the bedrooms make this home almost maintenance free and durable. Large yard is completely fenced in the front and back. Garage has been partially converted with tile floors so it can be used as a "Flex Space" if so desired. Newer roof from 2020 and fresh paint make the home bright and welcoming on the inside and out. Interior laundry room and the stainless steel appliances in the kitchen are just a few more features of this property. Close proximity to schools, grocery stores, restaurants, UF, bus routes and downtown Gainesville. Don't miss out on this opportunity, contact us now to schedule a showing!
